name: Paine Field Time Lapse
description:
Hey everyone, this is a short time lapse video of some of the work going on at Paine Field (KPAE/PAE). In the 5 minute time frame that I recorded this, the workers opened the cowlings on a Hainan Airlines 787, which I thought was pretty cool. I hope you enjoy the video :)

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
_____________________________________________________

Music is "Take a Chance" by Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
